    {
      "author": "arnita rosiana",
      "authorUrl": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109350488078243459606?hl=id",
      "rating": 5,
      "text": "Happened to stay in the hotel, and decided to ordered room service and dine-in instead. All of the food is good, from its nasi goreng, soto ayam, club sandwich, home made pizza, to its drinks. Generous portion(!) with standard cafe price. Great and fast service, available until supper. They have a good home band on Saturday night as well",
      "textTranslated": "Kebetulan menginap di hotel, dan memutuskan untuk memesan layanan kamar dan makan di dalam. Semua makanannya enak, mulai dari nasi goreng, soto ayam, club sandwich, pizza buatan sendiri, hingga minumannya. Porsinya banyak (!) dengan harga kafe standar. Pelayanannya bagus dan cepat, tersedia hingga makan malam. Mereka juga memiliki band lokal yang bagus pada Sabtu malam.",
      "date": "2022-08-20T13:33:35.030Z",
      "relativeDate": "3 tahun lalu",
      "likesCount": 0,
